description: One of the rare small ships manufactured by luxury builder Van Hummel, the Royal Flush is used to shuttle VIP passengers between one expensive location and another. The ship lacks a reactor but is extremely nimble on RCS, boasting two wings with six thrusters each and a Miura intake regulator.
